message.body: #####, I apologize for the inconvenience but it appears that I will be headed into a birth in the next few hours and think it best to reschedule so as no
t to disrupt your day. I am completely free Monday and Tuesday during the day and hope we can find time then? Let me know. Enjoy your day!
No problem! Saves you from our not-really-ACed apt too :) I'll check with ##### abt Mon/Tues and get back to you.
Ok, Tuesday morning is best. Would 9:30 be okay? (Got 6 straight hours of sleep last night, amazing!)
Tuesday. 9:30. Perfect. Congrats on the sleep!!
